ithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/minimum-tasbih-ruku-sajda\/","url_meta":{"origin":34861,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorifying Allah minimum three times in bowing, prostrating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you bows in prayer, let him say three times in his bowing: Glory be to my Lord, the Greatest. He will have completed his bowing and that is the least of it. Let him say\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33026,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/prophets-dua-ruku-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":34861,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet&#8217;s supplication in bowing, prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say in his bowing and prostration, \u201cGlory be to you, Allah our Lord, and your praises. Forgive me.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4042, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 484 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_tex